@page "/features"

<PageTitle>Features</PageTitle>

<main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="eyebrow">Core capabilities</div>
        <h1>Features built for <span class="gradient-text">stable execution</span></h1>
        <p>Kohinoor EA is designed for traders who want a reliable MT4 trading workflow with automation, structure, and control.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container feature-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Fully Automated</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA automates market monitoring, trade execution, and position management. Once installed and configured, it can operate according to programmed logic without constant manual input.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Risk Management</h3>
          <p>Effective risk control is a core part of the system. It uses money management principles and trade handling logic to help control exposure while allowing users to adjust settings to their preferences.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Works on MT4</h3>
          <p>Developed for the widely trusted MetaTrader 4 platform, Kohinoor EA integrates smoothly with MT4-compatible broker accounts and familiar charting tools.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>High Accuracy Focus</h3>
          <p>The system prioritizes quality trade setups through structured market conditions and predefined filters intended to improve consistency and reduce unnecessary trades.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Easy Setup</h3>
          <p>The installation process is straightforward and the settings are accessible for both new and experienced traders, making deployment fast and practical.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>XAUUSD Pair Support</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA is optimized for XAUUSD (Gold), one of the most active instruments in the market, with logic designed for dynamic gold price movement.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container panel">
        <span class="badge">Why this matters</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Less screen time. More disciplined execution.</h2>
        <p>Automation does not remove control. It applies a structured process consistently while still allowing the trader to define account-level preferences and risk settings.</p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/pricing">Start Trading Now</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/contact">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div><strong>Kohinoor EA</strong></div>
      <div><p>Optimized for MT4 and XAUUSD with disciplined algorithmic logic.</p></div>
    </div>
  </footer>


